title: Coaching Up the Winners: An MFCEO Q&A, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO214
itunes:title: Coaching Up the Winners: An MFCEO Q&A, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO214
description: I’ve told you guys that my early years of business were rough. I made every mistake possible.I felt like an idiot working hard and getting no results. I hated it. So at some point I made a decision that when I “made it,” I was going to help people through those rough early years of entrepreneurship. In today's episode, I sit down with 7 entrepreneurs - the winners of our MFCEO testimonial contest - to answer their questions and provide some direction. They asked great question you're asking too.
